ee7056d7-75d1-4b99-b576-cba1026b02d8.title: Spirit Tree
ee7056d7-75d1-4b99-b576-cba1026b02d8.text:
You friend of gnome people, you friend of mine.
Would you like me to take you somewhere?

58eaa0a9-e76d-408e-b826-f75b801195b0.title: Spirit Tree
58eaa0a9-e76d-408e-b826-f75b801195b0.text: You can travel to the trees which are related to me.

942a62ef-9e53-48ae-a9c0-2060801ab229.title: Spirit Tree
942a62ef-9e53-48ae-a9c0-2060801ab229.text: You cannot travel to that land at this time.

b0011147-c620-494a-9f8d-b8849143eead.text: You must complete Song of the Elves to travel to Prifddinas.

7450fdb3-2e26-4a26-bb14-0c62482623e0.title: Spirit Tree
7450fdb3-2e26-4a26-bb14-0c62482623e0.text: None of my brethren are at that location.

0f93ebfb-b785-4cd9-ad5e-6a8d525d8d25.title: Spirit Tree
0f93ebfb-b785-4cd9-ad5e-6a8d525d8d25.text: None of my brethren are in your house.

5d7f3533-099c-438e-9efb-8ca26fe56f91.title: Spirit Tree

c01835bd-511e-4dfb-abee-2bd96073bc7d.text:

Waste.
